reviewText:
Girls of the South Eastern Colleges is 54 minutes long. You have fifteen girls representing eight states. These ladies waste no time in showing off their birthday suits. In one scene the ladies are washing cars in the nude. I will admit the video looks like it was shot in a studio and not at any college or university but still worth the 54 minutes. Girls of the South Eastern Colleges gets an AAAAA+++++.

Louisiana-Heather & Amanda
Florida-Stacy & Elise
Georgia-Martika & Shari
Alabama-Sara & Diana
Mississippi-Christine & Michelle
Tennessee-Kim
Arkansas-Christina & Alicia
Kentucky-Angela & Ellen
